{"tid":2170532,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲係會同賓周講嘢？","createTime":"2020-08-23T10:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T02:12:09.000Z","uid":51346,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a9517573690cdbf8da99ec3120faaa7bdea6fd42","tid":2170532,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:29:52.000Z","msg":"有時揀緊av會問佢呢套好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時打完就會同佢講對唔住 無辦法令佢成為幸福賓周<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過最癲係我會擰佢個頭面向自己講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（勃起咗做唔到 唔好試）"},{"pid":"e1e77f854c9bc684ac0b52bf89296bbecfba7a68","tid":2170532,"uid":36528,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:31:41.000Z","msg":"射完會講 辛苦晒喇兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bc42b275690fe584d8f99af3beb72f883cc2fe","tid":2170532,"uid":286155,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"唔會啦<br />\n佢講野邊個負責忍尿"},{"pid":"91070998272135be1eeae15078abd29355ee50eb","tid":2170532,"uid":160074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:34:34.000Z","msg":"幻想到個畫面，好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eb56ae5e4823f968e02d395f0a71fa5ddd78ba4","tid":2170532,"uid":51346,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e1e77f854c9bc684ac0b52bf89296bbecfba7a68","tid":2170532,"uid":36528,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:31:41.000Z","msg":"射完會講 辛苦晒喇兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:35:10.000Z","msg":"所以細個會叫佢做細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 親過親兄弟"},{"pid":"e5d17408104b792dc6a6f8139d5d8c0e7af9bb09","tid":2170532,"uid":50744,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T10:35:56.000Z","msg":"我成日同佢講<br />\